					h5.text-uppercase App Development
				div.col
					figure.figure
						img.img-fluid.figure-img.border src='https://via.placeholder.com/900x220.png'
					p I built the final version of the iOS app, with backend help from a second developer, and managed contractors who built the Android app. I provided most of the final artwork.

